Revision history for Test-UnixExit

0.03    2023-01-02
        Recommend the use of Test2::Tools::Command instead.

0.02    2021-09-27
        Add exit_is_nonzero to munge any non-zero exit code to 1. Remove
        autogenerated -T taint flag from the test files. Switch to
        Module::Build. More tests, better test coverage.

0.01    2016-12-27
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
